Class DiscreteNumericalVariableView

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.va.med.srcalc.web.view.VariableView
      • gov.va.med.srcalc.web.view.DiscreteNumericalVariableView
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DisplayItem

    public class DiscreteNumericalVariableView
extends VariableView
    This class represents the visible attributes of a DiscreteNumericalVariable in order to provide other attributes that are only necessary for display.
